    "Number of layers are 16 and each layer have 25 neurons in it.",
    "• For dense connection, they employ fully connection each 400 neurons to first hidden layer having 180 neurons which have 180 × 400 connections.",
    "• These 180 neurons are fully connected to the next hidden layer having 84 neurons size of 84 × 180 connections.",
    "• Finally the output layer will be of 10 × 10 which is fully connected to the previous layer size of 10 × 84 connections.The main disadvantage of LeNet-5 is at time padding technique is not used to it takes some extra effort to retain the size of the image.",
